{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/1.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Play as your favorite Bratz character and begin your globe-trotting adventure to become the world\u2019s best fashion reporter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Photo_CatWalk_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/3.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Start out in your hometown of Stilesville and choose your character from the original Bratz Pack \u2013 Yasmin, Cloe, Jade, or Sasha. Then blaze a trail as you chase the biggest style stories, take on quests to help new friends, and play scorchin\u2019 minigames full of bratitude!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Character_Customization_Bratz_Stores_Streetwear_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/2.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Your adventure will take you to some of the most stylish locations: Barcelona, Seoul, and to the Stylin' Soiree. As you get the latest scoop for Bratz Magazine, you can use the money you earn to shop for rockin\u2019 outfits, customize your characters, and set stylin\u2019 new trends. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Moving_throught_the_map_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Bratz_ENG_CalloutBanner4_v1.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>You\u2019ll see your social following grow as fans are wowed by your passion for fashion. Get ready to express yourself and turn some heads with the Bratz Pack!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Variation_of_the_activities_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as the girls with a passion for fashion \u2013 Yasmin, Cloe, Jade, and Sasha.<br></li><li>Explore, make new friends, play games, and take on quests while reporting for the coolest magazine. <br></li><li>Customize the Bratz with stylin\u2019 fashions that wow your social followers.<br></li><li>Your journey to become the best reporter will take you from Stilesville to Barcelona, to Seoul and the Stylin' Soiree.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Stilesville","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/4a6c002a7f6ad56eb8ad34e204995220c115d78a.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to Barcelona","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/3a203c927e1298b9065af2c26b698905db12dd38.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to Seoul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/6f04f60c45bea97596080dab908c4f96a2b1dd22.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to the The Stylin' Soiree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/a6a064cdfeb645cd9a650d29c5bff6cfaf2180a4.jpg"},{"name":"We will need a bigger wardrobe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/3f61acb74cd75429b1e0a73b59c8c693a8abf6e7.jpg"},{"name":"Scooter Race","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/7cbfc9fe28dab957b8f13ec5401d0984d0341664.jpg"},{"name":"Roller Race","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/07bb22896a05ad87943ca55056e0def41d64b25b.jpg"},{"name":"Hoverboard Race","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/96227eac3e3caab1c7140d9eec539b87e45daee1.jpg"},{"name":"Talented Performer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/9eae7df4a038109f402c500bbf44b5f0813f2675.jpg"},{"name":"Born to Win","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2088340/78276f2f0b95f49c4ddfc2604429d30ffed4baf1.jpg"}],"total":19},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726743518","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/page.bg.jpg?t=1726743518","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726743518","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726743518","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Super Stylin' Update</h1><p>Hey Bratz Pack! We\u2019ve got a sizzlin\u2019 new free update available! It features some cool improvements, thanks to the awesome feedback from our players! <br><br>New additions:  <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blaze trails with all the girls, switching between Yasmin, Cloe, Jade, and Sasha at any time from their apartments. <br></li><li>Have more fun at the Stylin\u2019 Soiree and complete this level in style. Continue to shine on your quest to collect more treasure and unlock achievements. <br></li><li>Capture and re-live the fun moments - flick through your brand-new photo gallery where you can store 10-12 snaps. <br></li><li>New photo spots throughout the cities! Snap the whole Bratz Pack together in scorchin\u2019 poses.</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/1.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Play as your favorite Bratz character and begin your globe-trotting adventure to become the world\u2019s best fashion reporter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Photo_CatWalk_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/3.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Start out in your hometown of Stilesville and choose your character from the original Bratz Pack \u2013 Yasmin, Cloe, Jade, or Sasha. Then blaze a trail as you chase the biggest style stories, take on quests to help new friends, and play scorchin\u2019 minigames full of bratitude!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Character_Customization_Bratz_Stores_Streetwear_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/2.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>Your adventure will take you to some of the most stylish locations: Barcelona, Seoul, and to the Stylin' Soiree. As you get the latest scoop for Bratz Magazine, you can use the money you earn to shop for rockin\u2019 outfits, customize your characters, and set stylin\u2019 new trends. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Moving_throught_the_map_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Bratz_ENG_CalloutBanner4_v1.png?t=1726743518\" /><br><br>You\u2019ll see your social following grow as fans are wowed by your passion for fashion. Get ready to express yourself and turn some heads with the Bratz Pack!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/extras/Variation_of_the_activities_Bratz_Stores_Gif.gif?t=1726743518\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as the girls with a passion for fashion \u2013 Yasmin, Cloe, Jade, and Sasha.<br></li><li>Explore, make new friends, play games, and take on quests while reporting for the coolest magazine. <br></li><li>Customize the Bratz with stylin\u2019 fashions that wow your social followers.<br></li><li>Your journey to become the best reporter will take you from Stilesville to Barcelona, to Seoul and the Stylin' Soiree.</li></ul>","developers":["Petoons Studio"],"dlc":[2281810,2451150],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088340/header.jpg?t=1726743518","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 MGA Entertainment, INC. BRATZ\u2122 is a trademark of MGA in the U.S. and other countries. All logos, names, characters, likenesses, images, slogans, and packaging appearance are all property of MGA. User under license by Outright Games Limited. Published by Outright Games Limited. Software \u00a9 2022 Outright Games Limited. Developed by Petoons Studio Ltd. All Rights Reserved.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256942442,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256942442/movie480.mp4?t=1683875593","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256942442/movie_max.mp4?t=1683875593"},"name":"Super Stylin' Update PEGI","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256942442/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1683875593","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256942442/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1683875593","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256942442/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1683875593"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256913808,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic